mlogic.algos.analysis

Class OrderOfGrowthEstimator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mlogic.algos.analysis.OrderOfGrowthEstimator

  • public class OrderOfGrowthEstimator
extends java.lang.Object
    WIP...

    Helps classifies an X-Y data set into one of the following growth classes:

    • Constant - O(1)
    • Logarithmic - O(log n)
    • Linear - O(n)
    • Linearithmic - O(n log n)
    • Poly - O(poly n)
    • Exponential - O(exp n)

    Author:
    Rajaram G
